ilson|first=Richard Guy|chapter=Art Deco in the USA |title=Grove Art Online|date=2015|publisher=Oxford University Press |url=https://doi.org/10.1093/gao/9781884446054.article.T2283819 |accessdate=2018-04-06 }} *{{cite book|last=Woodham | first=Jonathan M. |title=A Dictionary of Modern Design |url=http://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780192800978.001.0001/acref-9780192800978-e-28 |chapter=American Union of Decorative Artists and Craftsmen |publisher=Oxford University Press |year= 2016 |isbn=9780191726767 |accessdate=2018-04-06 }}
